{
  "texts": [
    "A semi-structured interview guide assessed participants' knowledge and opinions on AI-driven personalization, chatbots, and virtual assistants for customer experience.",
    "The interview approach allowed participants to provide thorough responses and insights with open-ended questions.",
    "Participants were asked about phishing, ransomware, and data invasions during interviews.",
    "They were also asked about security measures to prevent these attacks.",
    "Participants were also asked to forecast cyberattacks and security measures."
  ]
}